 they can afford them.  Through their selection of cards to buy, and how they play their hands as they draw them, the players construct their deck on the fly, striving for the most efficient path to the precious victory points by game end.<br/><br/>Dominion is not a CCG, but the play of the game is similar to the construction and play of a CCG deck. The game comes with 500 cards. You select 10 of the 25 Kingdom card types to include in any given play&mdash;leading to immense variety.<br/><br/>&mdash;user summary<br/><br/>Part of the Dominion series.<br/><br/>"]} {:tag :thumbnail, :attrs nil, :content ["https://cf.geekdo-images.com/j6iQpZ4XkemZP07HNCODBA__thumb/img/B2u2ghwlmI_qsUtCwuvcbnBcIqU=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic394356.jpg"]} {:tag :image, :attrs nil, :content ["https://cf.geekdo-images.com/j6iQpZ4XkemZP07HNCODBA__original/img/96COuakNiLRrjDLc1sM4Zxsw4WE=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic394356.jpg"]} {:tag :boardgamepublisher, :attrs {:objectid "3"}, :content ["Rio Grande Games"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "288361"}, :content ["022 – The one thing you need to know as a Game Designer"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "21416"}, :content ["2008 Meeples' Choice Award"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "20827"}, :content ["2008 Origins Awards Best Traditional Card Game Winner"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "20330"}, :content ["2009 As d'Or - Jeu de l'Année Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "19822"}, :content ["2009 Deutscher Spiele Preis Best Family/Adult Game Winner"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "13348"}, :content ["2009 Diana Jones Award for Excellence in Gaming Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "13349"}, :content ["2009 Diana Jones Award for Excellence in Gaming Winner"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "8937"}, :content ["2009 Fairplay À la carte Winner"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "8414"}, :content ["2009 Golden Geek Best 2-