rk force to various tasks. You'll need to buy paint, mix paint, work on painting the fresco, raise money (which you'll need to buy the aforementioned paint!) by painting portraits, and perhaps even send your apprentices to the opera in order to increase their happiness. Points are scored mostly by painting the fresco, which requires specific combinations of paints, so you'll need to buy and mix your paints wisely, in addition to beating other players to the paints and fresco segments you would like to paint.<br/><br/>Fresco includes several expansion modules, so you can play without expansions for a lighter family game or add in expansions to vary play and increase the decision-making and difficulty, resulting in a very flexible game with a high replay value.<br/><br/>"]} {:tag :thumbnail, :attrs nil, :content ["https://cf.geekdo-images.com/DCVRR-zA7Jy9wjuZudTZ8w__thumb/img/7-_wICvkH7Opfpkc4vkNYvubia4=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic714398.jpg"]} {:tag :image, :attrs nil, :content ["https://cf.geekdo-images.com/DCVRR-zA7Jy9wjuZudTZ8w__original/img/dF1pDf3JLgqAdzD9uhy14Pd3yx8=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic714398.jpg"]} {:tag :boardgamepublisher, :attrs {:objectid "47"}, :content ["Queen Games"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "19685"}, :content ["2010 Deutscher Spiele Preis Best Family/Adult Game Winner"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "8751"}, :content ["2010 Golden Geek Best Board Game Artwork/Presentation Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "8755"}, :content ["2010 Golden Geek Best Family Board Game Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "21195"}, :content ["2010 Gouden Ludo Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "24307"}, :content ["2010 Graf Ludo Best Family Game Graphics Winner"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "12826"}, :content ["2010 International Gamers Awards - General Strategy; Multi-player Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "19004"}, :content ["2010 Japan Boar