ir captain is killed.  Points due to gold are hidden so there's some uncertainty about when the game will end.<br/><br/>A big component of the game is whether (or when) to turn &quot;pirate&quot; or remain as a trader or neutral party. Both careers are fraught with danger: pirates are hunted by NPCs (and other players) for their bounty and blocked to certain ports while traders are hunted by non-player pirates as well as their opponents and generally have to sacrifice combat capability for cargo capacity.  Although players can kill each other, there is no player elimination as players may draw a new captain (with a penalty) so it's possible to come back from defeat.<br/><br/>"]} {:tag :thumbnail, :attrs nil, :content ["https://cf.geekdo-images.com/RmKYojYHmV8X-ebtNgaz-g__thumb/img/Rd6POAEmJOEtwKB7bSDTKPsL_9k=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic738119.jpg"]} {:tag :image, :attrs nil, :content ["https://cf.geekdo-images.com/RmKYojYHmV8X-ebtNgaz-g__original/img/wrLHO6mElyCGzog0aHzJ9KE-SeE=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic738119.jpg"]} {:tag :boardgamepublisher, :attrs {:objectid "538"}, :content ["Z-Man Games"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "13896"}, :content ["2011 Golden Geek Best Board Game Artwork/Presentation Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "14830"}, :content ["2011 Golden Geek Best Board Game Artwork/Presentation Winner"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "13905"}, :content ["2011 Golden Geek Best Thematic Board Game Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "18780"}, :content ["2011 JoTa Best Artwork Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "18783"}, :content ["2011 JoTa Best Wargame Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "14614"}, :content ["2011 Lucca Games Best Boardgame for Experts"]} {:tag :boardgamedesigner, :attrs {:objectid "7627"}, :content ["Kasper Aagaard"]} {:tag :boardgamemechanic, :attrs {:objectid "2001"}, :content ["Action Points"]} {:tag :boardgamecategory, :attrs {:objecti