ine cards), and filling wine orders (wine order cards). Players work towards the goal of running the most successful winery in Tuscany.<br/><br/>"]} {:tag :thumbnail, :attrs nil, :content ["https://cf.geekdo-images.com/WrnWFA1Sysm3-nQyBe1sUA__thumb/img/udscIXtuApQ6rFYHjfAM5zMKfFs=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic2619743.jpg"]} {:tag :image, :attrs nil, :content ["https://cf.geekdo-images.com/WrnWFA1Sysm3-nQyBe1sUA__original/img/cGg9S0AH41VxczdybvFsb81AKWw=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic2619743.jpg"]} {:tag :boardgamepublisher, :attrs {:objectid "23202"}, :content ["Stonemaier Games"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "240120"}, :content ["#13: We're Still Right"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "180589"}, :content ["#19: Viticulture on tap, Quadropolis &amp; TableTop Day"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "189980"}, :content ["#30: Stephen Buonocore interview; The Dragon &amp; Flagon on tap; Dice City &amp; Viticulture"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "155041"}, :content ["#84 – Tabletop – Scythe with Jamey Stegmaier"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "288361"}, :content ["022 – The one thing you need to know as a Game Designer"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "334092"}, :content ["046 – A Walkthrough of Jamey Stegmaier’s proven Game Design Process"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "61145"}, :content ["2013 Board Game Quest Awards Best Strategy/Euro Game Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "61147"}, :content ["2013 Board Game Quest Awards Game of the Year Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "174614"}, :content ["3. Devon Dice Podcast Presents... a review of 2015 part 1"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "181093"}, :content ["9. Devon Dice Podcast - The Gallerist Review  and more"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "181355"}, :content ["ba005 – Altes Dorf in neuen Schl