 the game ends with players receiving extra victory points for having trading posts in Beijing, fulfilling the most orders, and having trading posts in the cities on secret city cards that each player gets at the start of the game.<br/><br/>This game should not be confused with Marco Polo Expedition, which has the same German title.<br/><br/>"]} {:tag :thumbnail, :attrs nil, :content ["https://cf.geekdo-images.com/n1G7_aWToLAAB7Mqt8iwyA__thumb/img/qfEgrXBN5L1EeMQ91siw6r_OoL4=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic2461346.png"]} {:tag :image, :attrs nil, :content ["https://cf.geekdo-images.com/n1G7_aWToLAAB7Mqt8iwyA__original/img/VQddnfi_QO0r4GmUU3M8_-nuO3Q=/0x0/filters:format(png)/pic2461346.png"]} {:tag :boardgamepublisher, :attrs {:objectid "133"}, :content ["Hans im Glück"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "367592"}, :content ["#143: Pace Yourself"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "245176"}, :content ["#31: SEAL Team Flix and Getting Rid of Games"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "271727"}, :content ["#49: Crusaders and Thematic Disconnects"]} {:tag :boardgamepodcastepisode, :attrs {:objectid "285440"}, :content ["#62: A Melange of Games to Play Again"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "46044"}, :content ["2015 Cardboard Republic Tactician Laurel Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "28189"}, :content ["2015 Deutscher Spiele Preis Best Family/Adult Game Winner"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "34510"}, :content ["2015 Golden Geek Best Strategy Board Game Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "34500"}, :content ["2015 Golden Geek Board Game of the Year Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "37767"}, :content ["2015 International Gamers Award - General Strategy: Multi-player Nominee"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attrs {:objectid "28163"}, :content ["2015 International Gamers Award - General Strategy: Multi-player Winner"]} {:tag :boardgamehonor, :attr